{"tid":580791,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"投入過多 無謂浪費錢 無謂創科","createTime":"2018-03-04T19:12:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T14:28:51.000Z","uid":36341,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2c466876eae9a9ba9f239a92b4c58edfdef3c622","tid":580791,"uid":36341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T19:12:49.000Z","msg":"投入過多　無謂浪費錢　無謂創科<br />\n預算陳茂波　終於癲了<br />\n要幫不幫　卻揀OP　來料<br />\n<br />\n窮盡知識　而浪費太多　培育太少<br />\n直到場大考　即將考了<br />\n免金考試　眾多考生　狂掉<br />\n<br />\n豪用公帑　人們勤納稅真的傷了<br />\n世間人　未救返　太有錢　無視需要<br />\n無力得很　財爺能力我心想不了<br />\n                    <br />\n笑死人　未派飛　民怨破表<br />\n<br />\n人漸變多　無奈地冇多　財力太少<br />\n預計又要爭　公屋單位<br />\n滿足不多　難敵箇中　玄妙<br />\n<br />\n無奈太多　從任命錯多　成熟太少<br />\n常望你有招　減少空置<br />\n己經出招　未見有料　藏掉<br />\n<br />\n無力欣賞　明明還在說資金多了<br />\n有些人　實要幫　冇錢偏　唔合資格<br />\n而又多錢　從來能活卻怎麼幫了<br />\n<br />\n百種人　望你幫　做對太少"},{"pid":"9b8ef253aa3505e1695e27234bbd66d9cef3d150","tid":580791,"uid":34205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T19:16:54.000Z","msg":"如夢初醒獸"},{"pid":"fbb7e5d1877fab12adf796e87045ccbd133fcdba","tid":580791,"uid":78429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T19:34:02.000Z","msg":"黎明嘅越夜越有機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d14c08fe96e8be118c0244ba44d67b6bc04a5b5","tid":580791,"uid":36341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T19:50:24.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"829ca77d13de0506431ada13e0727c88d00b9a58","tid":580791,"uid":36341,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T01:50:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d6272fd67c8f8e426502f2d9db70e6010833abb9","tid":580791,"uid":36341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T02:22:52.000Z","msg":"手土"},{"pid":"cebc34f5f78291ed352fe43b83a4ea7f4afc6b58","tid":580791,"uid":36341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6272fd67c8f8e426502f2d9db70e6010833abb9